35 PUBLIC DEFENSE SERVICES, MAINE COMMISSION ON
36 Maine Commission on Public Defense Services Z112
37 Initiative: Provides ongoing funding to establish 5 Assistant Defender I positions, 2
38 Paralegal positions and one Legal Administrator position. These positions are primarily
39 responsible for providing indigent legal services to criminal defendants and parties in child
40 protective proceedings for whom another public defender, assigned counsel, contract
41 counsel or employed counsel is not available to represent the defendant or party and, to the
42 extent there is additional capacity, these positions may also represent other individuals who
